  <brief_title>Blood Glucose Self Monitoring and HbA1c Effects on Glucose Control</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Benefit of the Blood Glucose Self Monitoring and a Regular Three-monthly Hemoglobin A1c Profile in Patients With Type 2-diabetes and Conventional Insulin Therapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
